<div class="entry-content clear" style="height: auto !important;">
<div class="post-desc">
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Short Information :</strong> <a style="color: #ff0000;" href="https://sarkariresult.com.cm/up-police-si-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Uttar Pradesh Police Recruitment and Promotion Board (UPPRPB)</a> </span><span style="font-size: inherit;">has released the admit card for the post of Sub Inspector</span><span style="font-size: inherit;">. This recruitment was released for 4543 posts. Candidates Can Also Check All Details on Official <a style="color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;" href="https://sarkariresult.com.cm/up-police-si-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sarkari Result</a>, Applications for the</span><span style="font-size: inherit;"> UP Police SI</span><span style="font-size: inherit;"> Recruitment 2025 were accepted from August 12, 2025, to September 11, 2025. The written examination is going to be conducted on 14-15 March 2026. Candidates who had applied this form can download their</span><span style="font-size: inherit;"> UP Police SI Admit Card 2026 from the link given below.</span></span></p>
