<h1 class="entry-title"><span style="color: #ff00ff;">NTA NEET UG Correction Form 2026</span></h1>
<p><strong>Author:</strong> Sarkari Exam Team<br />
<strong>Tag:</strong> 12th Pass Admission Form</p>
</header>
<p><!-- .entry-header --></p>
<div class="entry-content clear" style="height: auto !important;">
<div class="post-desc">
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Short Information : </strong><a style="color: #ff0000;" href="https://neet.nta.nic.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">National Testing Agency (NTA)</a></span> has released the Correction Form Notice for the NTA NEET UG Admission 2026 on the official website of the NTA. Online registration process for NTA NEET UG Online Form 2026 has started from 08 February 2026. and the candidate can apply till 11 March 2026 Candidates must check the complete details for NTA NEET UG Admission Form 2026 which has given below.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="newtable1">
<table style="font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; width: 100%;" width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="4" width="100%">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">National Testing Agency (NTA)</span></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #008000;">NTA NEET UG Admission 2026</span></h2>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="pd-0" colspan="4" width="100%">
<h3 align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><b>Important Dates</b></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Application Start Date : <strong>08 February 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Last Date : <strong>11 March 2026 (Extended)</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Fee Payment Last Date : <strong>11 March 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Correction Date : <strong>12-14 March 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">NEET UG 2026 Exam Date : <strong>03 May 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Admit Card Available : <strong>29 April 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Result Declared Date :<strong> June 2026</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 12pt;">Result :<strong> June 2025 Tentetive</strong></span></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="pd-0" colspan="4" width="100%">
<h3 align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><b>Application Fee</b></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">General : <strong>Rs. 1700/-</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">EWS, OBC : <strong>Rs. </strong><strong>1600/-</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">SC, ST, PH : <strong>Rs. </strong><b>1000</b>/-</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Out Side India : <strong>Rs. </strong><strong>9500/-</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;">Candidates have to pay their Examination Fee Through Debit Card / Credit Card / Net Banking / UPI and Other Fee Payment Mode Only.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="pd-0" colspan="4" width="100%">
<h3 align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><b>NTA NEET UG Admissions 2026 : Age Limit</b></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;"><strong>Born on or before 31 December 2009</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Minimum Age<strong> : 17 Years</strong></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Maximum Age<strong> : No Limit </strong></span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;">Age Relaxation as per NTA NEET UG Online Form Rules.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Use <span style="color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00;"><a style="color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00;" href="https://sarkariresulttools.net/age-calculator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><strong>Age Calculate</strong></a> </span>Tool &#8211; <a href="https://sarkariresulttools.net/age-calculator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><strong>Click Here</strong></a></span></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="pd-0" colspan="4" width="100%">
