<ul>
<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #008000;"><strong>Course Name </strong></span>: National Eligibility Cum Entrance Test NEET UG 2026</span></li>
<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Exam Name</span> </strong>: National Eligibility Cum Entrance Test, 2026 (NTA)</span></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
