<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Bihar Advt No. : 01-04/2022 Short Details of Notification</span></h2>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="pd-0" colspan="4" width="100%">
<h3 align="center"><span style="color: #000000;"><b>Important Dates</b></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Application Begin : <b>20 September 2022</b></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Last Date for Apply Online : <b>20 October 2022</b></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Pay Exam Fee Last Date :<b> 20 October 2022</b></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Court Reader, Steno Exam Date : <b>17 December 2023</b></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Admit Card Available :<b> 10 December 2023</b></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Court Reader Final Result : <b>12 September 2024</b></span></li>
<li><span style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Exam Date : <strong>22 December 2024</strong></span></li>
